{"tid":2387214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"SIM卡檔主：起碼一半做唔住","createTime":"2021-01-30T07:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T07:01:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bb07fa26775ed7fe85947a85392232e070a5e14f","tid":2387214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:01:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210130/7SNSMDVVJFATRLP5PCLQ77N4QE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210130%2F7SNSMDVVJFATRLP5PCLQ77N4QE%2F&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=d6afabc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210130%2F7SNSMDVVJFATRLP5PCLQ77N4QE%2F&h=dcf8b7fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210130/7SNSMDVVJFATRLP5PCLQ77N4QE/</a><br />\n<br />\nSIM卡檔主：起碼一半做唔住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sboSfIWFaqDeHxUlWH10I8DUZKQ=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2WW7C3N7GNEQTB224XDU7WXNYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsboSfIWFaqDeHxUlWH10I8DUZKQ%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2WW7C3N7GNEQTB224XDU7WXNYY.jpg&h=263546eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■實名制對售賣電話卡的攤檔影響極大。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自詡自由經濟體的香港，正火速與獨裁政體接軌，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港府效大陸 突推電話卡實名制  滅罪為名監控港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「冇嘢搵嘢做」<br />\n<br />\n政府聲稱措施有助打擊罪案，許則批評政府措施目的為取得市民個人資料，「冇嘢搵嘢做」。他並指電話卡零售商一般要向很多代理購入電話卡，「如果我同十幾廿個代理登記，係咪有十幾廿個system（登記系統）去做？」政府聲稱不會規管漫遊卡，但他質疑：「咁如果個號碼係可以打返香港嘅又使唔使登記呢？」<br />\n<br />\n根據諮詢文件，發出電。。。。。。。。"}]}